quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  51,7,"By the heaven comprising interwoven tracks,"
  51,8,"indeed, you<sup>pl </sup>are of different opinions{1}.",footnotes:1:Different opinions about the judgment.
  51,9,"Averted from it is he who is averted."
  51,10,"May the conjecturers perish!{1}",footnotes:1:Literally ‘May the conjecturers be killed’.
